## Análise Detalhada — Família C (Compute Optimized)

### Phase 3.1 (Dynamic Provisioning)
| Métrica | Serial (c5.large) | Horizontal (10× c5.large) | Vertical (c5.4xlarge) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Total** | 192.62s (3.21 min) | 211.38s (3.52 min) | **127.66s (2.13 min)** |
